# This GSEA was obtained using scStudio: https://compbio.imm.medicina.ulisboa.pt/app/scStudio 
# Genes were ranked based on average Log2 fold-change of the group of interest vs remaining macrophages
gsea <- readRDS("/mnt/nmorais-nfs/marta/shiny/scstudio/tokens/karine/gsea.rds")
gsea$r0.4_1vsOthers[[1]]
names(gsea)
##  [1] "r0.4_3vs5"            "r0.4_7vs4"            "r0.4_3vs2"           
##  [4] "r0.5_7vs1"            "r0.4_5-6vsOther"      "r0.4_1vsOthers"      
##  [7] "r0.4_3vsOthers"       "r0.4_7vsOthers"       "r0.5_7vsOthers"      
## [10] "r0.4_8vsOthers"       "r1.5_6vs2"            "rs0.4_2vsOthers"     
## [13] "rs0.4_2vs5"           "rs0.4_3vs5"           "rs0.4_2vs0"          
## [16] "rs0.4_5vsOthers"      "rs0.4_6vsOthers"      "rs0.4_1vs3"          
## [19] "res0.4_3vs0"          "rs0.4_0vsOthers"      "rs0.4_4vsOthers"     
## [22] "r0.4_3and7vsOt"       "r0.4_3and7vsOt_wiki"  "r0.4_3and7vsOt_kegg" 
## [25] "r0.4_3and8vsOt"       "r0.4_3and8vsOt_kegg"  "r0.4_3and8vsOt_GO"   
## [28] "r0.4_3and8vsOt_HKegg" "r0.4_6vsOt_HKegg"     "r0.4_3vsOt_hkegg"    
## [31] "r0.4_3vs6"
df <- data.frame(pathway = c(gsea$r0.4_1vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$r0.4_3vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$r0.4_7vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$r0.4_8vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$rs0.4_2vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$rs0.4_5vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$rs0.4_5vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$rs0.4_6vsOthers[[1]]$pathway,
                             gsea$rs0.4_0vsOthers[[1]]$pathway),
                 
                 padj = c(gsea$r0.4_1vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$r0.4_3vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$r0.4_7vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$r0.4_8vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$rs0.4_2vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$rs0.4_5vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$rs0.4_4vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$rs0.4_6vsOthers[[1]]$padj,
                          gsea$rs0.4_0vsOthers[[1]]$padj),
                 
                 NES = c(gsea$r0.4_1vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$r0.4_3vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$r0.4_7vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$r0.4_8vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$rs0.4_2vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$rs0.4_5vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$rs0.4_4vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$rs0.4_6vsOthers[[1]]$NES,
                         gsea$rs0.4_0vsOthers[[1]]$NES),

                 cluster = factor(c(rep(1, 50),
                                    rep(3,50),
                                    rep(7,50),
                                    rep(8,50),
                                    rep(2,50),
                                    rep(5,50),
                                     rep(4,50),
                                    rep(6,50),
                                    rep(0,50))))
df
regulation <- df$NES
regulation[regulation > 0] <- "UP"
regulation[regulation < 0] <- "DOWN"
regulation[regulation == 0] <- "NONE"
df$regulation <- regulation
df
df$pathway <- gsub("_", " ", df$pathway)
df$pathway <- gsub("HALLMARK", "", df$pathway)
df <- df[order(df$pathway, decreasing = FALSE),]
df
write.table(df, "/mnt/nmorais-nfs/marta/pA_karine/r_session/integrated_analysis_revised/paper-figures/tables/S4E_table.txt", sep = "\t", quote = FALSE, append = FALSE)
ggplot(df)+
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x= cluster, 
                           y = pathway, 
                           color=regulation, 
                           size=-log10(padj+ 10**-9))) + 
  theme_classic() + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(size = 17)) +
  scale_color_manual(values=c("blue","red"))+
   scale_y_discrete(limits=rev) +ylab("") + xlab("")
